# Monorepo Release Mode / Monorepo 发布模式

- Focus / 聚焦: reproducible CI, release gates, and rollback readiness.
- Workspace discipline / 工作区纪律: install deps with `pnpm --filter`.
- Evidence-driven / 证据驱动: mark tasks done only with commit/CI/script evidence.

## Mandatory Checks / 强制检查

- Keep CI gates complete: lint + type-check + test + build.
- For release changes, verify smoke + rollback paths.
- Avoid unpinned infra/runtime versions in compose/workflow.

## Delivery Style / 交付方式

- Update `todo.md` with timestamps when milestones complete.
- External dependencies remain unchecked and listed as blockers.
